ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I'd totally recommend this class, just prepare yourself to be worked to the bone. It's an incredible overview of a 100 years+ of history from so many different angles. I'd recommend this if you're interested in Eastern Europe, I'd recommend it if you're interested in history, if you're interested in humanity, whatever. It's an incredible survey of the people of a whole region. A truly remarkable class.
